com.wm.app.b2b.client.cache.config

Class SearchResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wm.app.b2b.client.cache.config.SearchResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SearchResult
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The com.wm.app.b2b.client.cache.config package contains the class that wraps the cache search results. The information available in the results are key, value, aggregated results, and predefined attributes of the selected entry from the target cache. The aggregated results based on the aggregated function are used with the search query. The attributes that are returned as part of the search results are based on the attributes included in the search query.
